    <rdfs:comment>Infers that any part with a DrillPress-processable feature requires a PeckDrilling step. Peck drilling (G83, controlled by the Q retraction parameter) periodically withdraws the drill to break chips and let coolant reach the cutting edge. Mandatory for the deep holes found in aerospace thick stock (depth greater than ~3x drill diameter).</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:label>DrillPress_PeckDrilling</rdfs:label>
