    <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">FormingStage</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Manufacturing stage grouping (PIBITI extension). Stage grouping for precedence: CuttingStage -&gt; HoleMakingStage -&gt; FormingStage -&gt; FinishingStage -&gt; SurfaceTreatmentStage. Drilling subclasses (SpotDrilling/PeckDrilling/Reaming) inherit HoleMakingStage via mfg:Drilling.</rdfs:comment>
  </rdf:Description>
