    <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/rafab/ontologies/manufacturing_core#Drilling"/>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Deep-hole drilling with incremental retractions (G83, peck=Q parameter). Breaks chips and allows coolant to reach the cutting edge. Used for holes deeper than ~3x drill diameter, typical in aerospace thick stock.</rdfs:comment>
